# Week 30, 2026 (example — delete once a real note exists)

**Headline claim.** One sentence: the single most important thing that
moved, stated as a claim someone could disagree with.

**Mechanism.** Two or three sentences on why it moved, grounded in the
week's datapack (notes-inbox/), not general knowledge.

**What it does and doesn't imply.** Bound the reading explicitly. If the
spike is plausibly an anniversary artifact, say so.

**One number worth remembering.** E.g. "Shipping at 94 — its highest
percentile since the datapack began."
